%% Data Flow Diagram: vllm-orchestrator-gateway
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant LLM as vLLM / LLM Backend

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Authorization header (pass-through)
    Note over Gateway: Lookup route config<br/>Resolve detector list<br/>Inject "detectors" field into payload

    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (optional mTLS)<br/>Auth: mTLS client cert (if configured)<br/>Forwards: Authorization, X-Forwarded-* headers
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input detection<br/>(if detector.input=true)
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Chat completion request
    LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Output detection<br/>(if detector.output=true)
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with detections
    Note over Gateway: If detections found &<br/>route has fallback_message:<br/>replace content with fallback
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>{"stream": true}<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP (plaintext)
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>{"stream": true}<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (optional mTLS)
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input detection
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: Streaming chat completion

    loop SSE Stream
        LLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE data chunk
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Output detection per chunk
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Chunk detection results
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: event
        Note over Gateway: Parse SSE data line<br/>If detections & fallback:<br/>replace content, set finish_reason="stop"
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: event
    end

    Gateway-->>Client: SSE data: [DONE]
